5C%22%3EThe%20Daily%20Tribute%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20new%20operations%20would%20support%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20BRP%20Teresa%20Magbanua%2C%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pna.gov.ph%2Farticles%2F1173869%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewest%20and%20largest%3C%2Fa%3E%20patrol%20vessels%20deployed%20by%20the%20Philippine%20Coast%20Guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vessel%20has%20been%20operating%20around%20the%20island%20of%20Sabina%20Shoal%20since%20April%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20%26quot%3Badvancing%20our%20national%20interest%20and%20safeguarding%20our%20position%20at%20Escoda%20Shoal%2C%26quot%3B%20Trinidad%20said%2C%20using%20the%20island's%20Filipino%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensions%20have%20heightened%20between%20China%20and%20the%20Philippines%20over%20territorial%20claims%20over%20Sabina%20Shoal%2C%20a%20disputed%20atoll%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20where%20flashpoints%20have%20become%20more%20frequent%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Chinese%20coast%20guard%20armed%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphilippines-soldiers-bare-hands-fight-armed-china-coast-guard-swords-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eswords%20and%20knives%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20attacked%20Filipino%20vessels%20in%20the%20contested%20waters%2C%20resulting%20in%20injuries%20and%20one%20soldier%20losing%20a%20thumb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223165%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20Coast%20Guard%20holding%20knives%20and%20machetes%20as%20they%20approach%20Philippine%20troops%20in%20the%20Second%20Thomas%20Shoal%20at%20the%20disputed%20South%20China%20Sea%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667a8f5350b021b5cae90ba0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223158%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChinese%20Coast%20Guard%20holding%20knives%20and%20machetes%20as%20they%20approach%20Philippine%20troops%20in%20the%20disputed%20South%20China%20Sea%20on%20June%2017%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EArmed%20Forces%20of%20the%20Philippines%20via%20AP%2C%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20China's%20largest%20coastguard%20vessel%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeijings-monster-coastguard-ship-ramps-up-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edropped%20anchor%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Philippines'%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%2C%20which%20the%20Philippines%20described%20as%20an%20act%20of%20%26quot%3Bintimidation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20recently%20as%20last%20week%2C%20Philippine%20Coast%20Guard%20spokesperson%20Jay%20Tarriela%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fjaytaryela%2Fstatus%2F1828077854539874574%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20China%20had%20deployed%2040%20vessels%20to%20block%20its%20delivery%20of%20supplies%20to%20soldiers%20stationed%20in%20Sabina%20Shoal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20an%20X%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fjaytaryela%2Fstatus%2F1829795642484670573%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Tarriela%20said%20that%20a%20Chinese%20Coast%20Guard%20vessel%20had%20rammed%20and%20collided%20three%20times%20with%20the%20BRP%20Teresa%20Magbanua%2C%20damaging%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261c1bd47-5b43-4ffc-9b9b-fe620a655116%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutnumbered%20and%20outgunned%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20late%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Teresa%20Magbanua%20has%20been%20outnumbered%20by%20over%2050%20Chinese%20ships%2C%20including%20three%20Chinese%20Coast%20Guard%20vessels%2C%20two%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20Navy%20ships%2C%20one%20Chinese%20hospital%20vessel%2C%20one%20research%20ship%2C%20and%2047%20Chinese%20maritime%20militia%20vessels%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Daily%20Tribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Trinidad%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%2C%20for%20now%2C%20sending%20further%20naval%20assets%20remains%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BRP%20Teresa%20Magbanua%20%26quot%3Bwas%20deployed%20alone%3B%20we%20are%20watching%20it%20because%20there%20are%20reports%20of%20crushed%20corals%20being%20piled%20up%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fu-s-support-for-the-philippines-in-the-south-china-sea-12%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econdemned%3C%2Fa%3E%20what%20it%20describes%20as%20China's%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bescalatory%26quot%3B%20actions%20against%20%26quot%3Blawful%26quot%3B%20Philippine%20maritime%20operations%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Sabina%20Shoal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20coast%20guard%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Feng.mod.gov.cn%2Fxb%2FNews_213114%2FTopStories%2F16334938.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Philippine%20ship%20%26quot%3Billegally%26quot%3B%20entered%20Sabina%20Shoal%20on%20Saturday%20and%20%26quot%3Bdeliberately%26quot%3B%20crashed%20into%20a%20Chinese%20ship%20that%20was%20enforcing%20maritime%20rights%20under%20a%20routine%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20once%20again%20warn%20the%20Philippines%20to%20face%20reality%20and%20give%20up%20illusions%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%20Dejun%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20China%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20said.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BWithdrawing%20the%20ship%20immediately%20on%20its%20own%20is%20the%20only%20correct%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22284caa34-83c2-43b0-a60e-a59418a3bba9%5C%22%3EExhausting%20rivals%20and%20testing%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sari%20Arho%20Havr%C3%A9n%2C%20an%20associate%20fellow%20at%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20who%20specializes%20in%20China's%20foreign%20relations%2C%20China's%20provocations%20are%20meant%20to%20%26quot%3Bexhaust%26quot%3B%20neighboring%20countries%20into%20accepting%20its%20claims%20over%20contested%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Vietnam%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Brunei%2C%20and%20Taiwan%20also%20lay%20claim%20to%20parts%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20wants%20to%20change%20the%20status%20quo%20by%20force%20%E2%80%94%20exhaust%20the%20countries%20to%20give%20in%20to%20their%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-ax-attack-philippines-south-china-sea-grab-territory-experts-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollin%20Koh%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Institute%20of%20Defence%20and%20Strategic%20Studies%20at%20Singapore's%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20China%20wants%20to%20test%20how%20far%20the%20US%20will%20support%20one%20of%20its%20allies%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20is%20deliberately%20escalating%20the%20situation%2C%20with%20a%20likely%20intention%20to%20test%20how%20far%20Washington%20would%20support%20Manila%2C%26quot%3B%20Koh%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F08%2F27%2Fasia%2Fchina-philippines-new-flashpoint-sabina-shoal-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-warships-could-protect-pacific-allys-ships-from-china-admiral-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edefense%20treaty%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20in%201951%2C%20the%20US%20is%20supposed%20to%20come%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20the%20Philippines%20if%20an%20armed%20attack%20occurs%20on%20its%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdm.%20Samuel%20Paparo%2C%20head%20of%20the%20US%20Indo-Pacific%20Command%2C%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20that%20some%20limited%20support%20could%20be%2