3a0aa2340f8b8008b6a7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThree%20oil%20and%20gas%20rigs%20owned%20by%20Transocean%20Ltd%20sit%20idle%20in%20the%20Grand%20Harbor%20in%20Valletta%2C%20Malta%20October%2022%2C%202015.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FBalazs%20Koranyi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20boom%20could%20make%20oil%20supply%20rise%20and%20prices%20fall%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20could%20boost%20oil%20supply%20via%20improved%20logistics%20and%20productivity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20increase%20in%20supply%20will%20outweigh%20the%20rise%20in%20demand%20from%20AI's%20power%20needs%2C%20the%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20artificial%20intelligence%20boom%20could%20make%20oil%20prices%20fall%20even%20as%20the%20technology%20boosts%20power%20demand%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20analysts%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20point%20to%20AI's%20improved%20logistics%20capabilities%20and%20boost%20to%20oil%20recovery%2C%20which%20could%20increase%20oil%20supply%20and%20drive%20down%20prices%20in%20the%20next%20decade%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20forecast%20stands%20in%20contrast%20to%20predictions%20that%20energy%20prices%20will%20rise%20as%20demand%20for%20AI%20requires%20more%20power%20for%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20debate%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%20on%20energy%20and%20metals%20has%20mostly%20focused%20on%20the%20demand%20side%20given%20the%20expected%20boost%20to%20power%20demand.%20However%2C%20we%20highlight%20that%20AI%20may%20eventually%20weigh%20on%20oil%20prices%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20by%20boosting%20oil%20supply%20through%20two%20main%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20said%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20research%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20point%20first%20to%20AI's%20potential%20to%20reduce%20oil%20production%20costs%20by%20improving%20logistics%20and%20resource%20allocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20point%20to%20an%20example%20of%20oil%20rigs%20in%20North%20Dakota%2C%20where%20an%20oil%20company's%20use%20of%20AI-driven%20predictive%20and%20automated%20drilling%20reduced%20drilling%20times%20by%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssuming%20a%2025%25%20productivity%20gain%2C%20other%20early%20AI%20adopters%20could%20save%20%245%20per%20barrel%20in%20costs%2C%20the%20analysts%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20say%20AI%20could%20also%20boost%20recoverable%20resources%2C%20with%20a%20hypothetical%2010%25-20%25%20jump%20in%20recovering%20US%20shale%2C%20which%20could%20increase%20oil%20reserves%20by%208%25-20%25%2C%20or%20up%20to%2030%20billion%20barrels%2C%20they%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20supply%20gains%20greatly%20outweigh%20any%20potential%20boost%20in%20demand%2C%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%20Even%20as%20AI%20requires%20more%20power%2C%20that%20demand%20likely%20won't%20effect%20oil%20demand%20since%20oil%20is%20%26quot%3Bscarcely%20used%20as%20a%20source%20of%20energy%20for%20power%20generation%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20power%20generation%20demand%20will%20likely%20boost%20power%20and%20natural%20gas%20markets%2C%20they%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20AI-related%20increase%20in%20oil%20demand%20will%20likely%20come%20from%20higher%20incomes%2C%20which%20could%20raise%20prices%20by%20%242%20per%20barrel%2C%20the%20analysts%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20impact%20is%20minimal%20compared%20to%20how%20much%20electric%20vehicle%20adoption%20and%20lower%20natural%20gas%20prices%20will%20weigh%20on%20oil%20demand%2C%20while%20oil%20supply%20increases%20via%20the%20use%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaken%20together%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20AI%20would%20be%20a%20modest%20net%20negative%20to%20oil%20prices%20in%20the%20medium-to-long%20term%20as%20the%20negative%20impact%20from%20the%20cost%20curve%20(c.-%245%2Fbbl)%20-%20oil's%20long-term%20anchor%20-%20would%20outweigh%20the%20positive%20impacts%20from%20the%20demand%20side%20(c.%2B%241-2%2Fbbl)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-oil-prices-productivity-logistics-supply-demand-energy-goldman-sachs-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725453464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d76cc414a5cd1fcc8ce3ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fai-oil-prices-productivity-logistics-supply-demand-energy-goldman-sachs-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20impact%20to%20supply%20due%20to%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20could%20end%20up%20outweighing%20any%20rise%20in%20demand%20from%20AI's%20power%20needs%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20analysts%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kcloonan%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Cloonan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fai-oil-prices-productivity-logistics-supply-demand-energy-goldman-sachs-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98CBS%20Mornings%20Plus%E2%80%99%20Set%20for%20September%2030%20Debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725453240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFINAL-CBS-MORNINGS-PLUS-PHOTO.jpeg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236129478%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Morning-news%20viewers%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20will%20soon%20have%20more%20to%20watch%20on%20CBS.%20CBS%20News%20will%20on%20September%2030%20launch%20a%20live%2C%20third%20hour%20of%20its%20flagship%20%E2%80%9CCBS%20Mornings%E2%80%9D%20A.M.%20program%2C%20a%20move%20that%20will%20extend%20the%20show%20into%20the%209%20a.m.%20hour.%20%E2%80%9CCBS%20Mornings%20Plus%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20co-anchored%20by%20Tony%20Dokoupil%20%5B%E2%8