hua%20Sapien%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20even%20more%20important%2C%20he%20said%2C%20considering%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Super%20Hornet%20as%20the%20primary%20fighter%20type%20still%20for%20the%20US%20Navy%20has%20significantly%20less%20impressive%20kinematic%20performance%20itself%20than%20the%20J-20%20or%20J-16%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20carry%20the%20PL-15%20and%20PL-17.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM-174B%20gives%20US%20Navy%20carrier%20air%20wings%20a%20new%20ability%20to%20engage%20China's%20air%20force%20and%20naval%20aviation%20aircraft%20at%20a%20greater%20range%20than%20its%20predecessor%2C%20potentially%20closing%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ship-launched%20SM-6%20missile%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20RIM-174%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20a%20range%20of%20up%20to%20230%20miles%2C%20and%20it%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-warships-used-weapon-combat-first-destroy-iranian-missiles-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecombat%20for%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20fall%20against%20the%20Houthis.%20The%20missile%20is%20a%20three-in-one%20extended-range%20weapon%20for%20anti-air%20and%20anti-surface%20warfare.%20It's%20also%20able%20to%20kill%20ballistic%20missiles%20during%20the%20terminal%20phase%20of%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20air-to-air%20role%2C%20it%20brings%20some%20of%20those%20capabilities%20to%20bear%20in%20new%20ways%20to%20help%20the%20US%20match%20newer%20Chinese%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronk%20said%20the%20PL-17%20is%20probably%20most%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecomparable%20to%20the%20AIM-174B%2C%20but%20the%20Chinese%20weapon%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emight%20have%20a%20longer%20range%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20platforms%20that%20are%20primarily%20going%20to%20be%20carrying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Chinese%20fighter%20jet%20flies%20above%20with%20some%20decoy%20flares%20soaring%20behind%20it%20against%20a%20blue%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ba51c1b4912df3ae1adf0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221985%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20J-16%20fighter%20jet%20releases%20decoy%20flares%20during%20Changchun%20Air%20Show%20at%20Changchun%20Dafangshen%20Airport%20in%20Changchun%2C%20Jilin%20Province%20of%20China.%3Cp%3EZheng%20Shuai%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PL-17%20is%20a%20rather%20large%20missile%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twz.com%2Fmassive-pl-17-air-to-air-missile-seen-on-chinese-j-16-fighters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappeared%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Chinese%20J-16%20multirole%20strike%20fighter%20during%20development.%20More%20recently%2C%20amid%20indications%20it%20was%20approaching%20operational%20status%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20on%20the%20jet%20last%20December.%20China's%20J-16%20fighter%20jet%20is%20a%20highly%20capable%20fourth-generation%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM-174B%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20carried%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-super-hornet-fighter-jets-arrive-middle-east-report-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENavy's%20Super%20Hornets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Observers%20have%20noted%20that%20Super%20Hornets%20may%20have%20trouble%20carrying%20the%20AIM-174B%20due%20to%20its%20size%20and%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20the%20missile%20is%20likely%20five%20times%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20AIM-120D%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20the%20weapon%20could%20impact%20the%20jet's%20top%20speed%20and%20altitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20new%20missile%20provides%20valuable%20reach.%20In%20an%20air%20combat%20scenario%20with%20China%2C%20the%20AIM-174B%20could%20likely%20be%20most%20useful%20at%20disrupting%20China's%20kill%20chain%2C%20or%20the%20process%20by%20which%20a%20target%20is%20identified%2C%20targeted%2C%20and%20destroyed%20and%20which%20assets%20are%20involved%20in%20completing%20that%20task.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20missile%20could%20target%20China's%20airborne%20early%20warning%20and%20control%20aircraft%20that%20help%20set%20up%20those%20kill%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20gives%20American%20aircraft%20the%20ability%20to%20target%20rear%20assets%2C%20like%20Chinese%20bombers%20and%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%2C%20target%20acquisition%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20US%20Navy%20F%2FA-18E%20Super%20Hornet%20jets%20sit%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20the%20Nimitz-class%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Carl%20Vinson%20with%20the%20ocean%20in%20the%20background%20at%20nighttime.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d7749f1d8d2deb96b86b37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F%2FA-18E%20Super%20Hornet%2C%20assigned%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BStingers%26quot%3B%20of%20Strike%20Fighter%20Squadron%20(VFA)%20113%2C%20launches%20from%20the%20flight%20deck%20of%20Nimitz-class%20aircraft%20carrier%20USS%20Carl%20Vinson%20(CVN%2070)%20while%20underway%20in%20the%20U.S.%203rd%20Fleet%20area%20of%20operations.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%202nd%20Class%20Isaiah%20B.%20Goessl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20air-to-air%20missile%20range%20game%20is%20expected%20to%20continue%20though.%20As%20the%20Pentagon%20noted%20in%20its%20report%2C%20China%20is%20at%20work%20on%20its%20air-to-air%20missiles%2C%20and%20the%20US%20is%20likewise%20working%20on%20next-generation%20systems%20like%20the%20AIM-260.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEstimates%20on%20exactly%20how%20the%20new%20AIM-174B%20and%20China's%20missiles%20could%20perform%20are%20based%20on%20publicly%20available%20data%20and%20understanding%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20knowledge%20of%20how%20the%20missile%20would%20actually%20perform.%20But%20even%20the%20weapon's%20existence%20could%20be%20enough%20to%20be%20useful%20to%20the%20US%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeterrence%2C%26quot%3B%20Bronk%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20about%20affecting%20your%20opponent's%20calculations%2C%20so%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20there's%20inevitably%20going%20to%20be%20a%20degree%20of%20ambiguity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-us-air-air-missile-closes-answers-china-weapons-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725450422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d72f7c14a5cd1fcc8caa4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-us-air-air-missile-closes-answers-china-weapons-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20been%20developing%20air-to-air%20missiles%20with%20increasingly%20greater%20range.%20The%20US%20Navy%20seems%20to%20have%20an%20answer%20in%20the%20AIM-174B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-us-air-air-missile-closes-answers-china-weapons-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranbir%20sings%20on%20'Rockstar'%20sets%3B%20fans%20react-%20WATCH%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725450375000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113063171%2Cimgsize-25598.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbts-video-of-ranbir-kapoor-singing-on-the-sets-of-rockstar-goes-viral-sparks-hilarious-reactions-from-fans-watch%2Farticleshow%2F113063171.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113063171.cms%5C%22%20hspac