ne-launched-in-india-check-price-specs-more-124090400777_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Fgadgets%2Fsamsung-galaxy-a06-smartphone-launched-in-india-check-price-specs-more-124090400777_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Any%20agreement%20only%20happens%20if%20...%20'%3A%20What%20Cong%20said%20on%20alliance%20with%20AAP%20for%20Haryana%20poll%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725449638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113064103%2Cimgsize-1066651.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fany-agreement-only-happens-if-what-congress-leader-said-on-alliance-with-aap-for-haryana-polls%2Farticleshow%2F113063673.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deepak%20Babaria%20of%20Congress%20stated%20that%20an%20alliance%20with%20AAP%20for%20the%20Haryana%20elections%20will%20proceed%20only%20if%20mutually%20beneficial%2C%20with%20a%20decision%20expected%20in%20two-three%20days.%20CPIM%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20have%20also%20shown%20interest%20in%20an%20alliance.%20Elections%20in%20Haryana%20are%20on%20October%205%2C%20and%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20October%208.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fany-agreement-only-happens-if-what-congress-leader-said-on-alliance-with-aap-for-haryana-polls%2Farticleshow%2F113063673.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan%20We%20Be%20So%20Rigid%3F%26quot%3B%20Top%20Court%20Grills%20Central%20Agency%20In%20Documents%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20tough%20questions%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20questioning%20if%20the%20agency's%20refusal%20to%20provide%20the%20accused%20with%20documents%20seized%20during%20a%20money%20laundering%20probe%20does%20not%20violate%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%2C%20Justice%20A%20Amanullah%20and%20Justice%20AG%20Masih%20was%20hearing%20an%20appeal%20related%20to%20the%20supply%20of%20documents%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20The%202022%20Sarla%20Gupta%20vs%20ED%20case%20pertains%20to%20the%20question%20on%C2%A0whether%20the%20investigating%20agency%20can%20deprive%20the%20accused%20of%20crucial%20documents%20it%20is%20relying%20on%20in%20a%20PMLA%20case%20in%20the%20pre-trial%20stage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20has%20come%20under%20the%20spotlight%20in%20several%20high-profile%20cases%20after%20top%20politicians%2C%20including%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20his%20Jharkhand%20counterpart%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20AAP%20leader%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20BRS%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%2C%20were%20arrested%20under%20this%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20court%20asked%20if%20the%20accused%20can%20be%20denied%20the%20document%20solely%20on%20a%20technical%20ground.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20everything%20be%20transparent%3F%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Amanullah%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20ED%2C%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20accused%20knows%20that%20there%20are%20documents%2C%20he%20can%20ask%2C%20but%20if%20he%20does%20not%20know%20and%20just%20has%20assumption%2C%20he%20cannot%20seek%20a%20roving%20enquiry%20on%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20asked%20if%20this%20won't%20violate%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20guarantees%20right%20to%20life%20and%20liberty.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20in%20a%20PMLA%20case%2C%20you%20may%20retrieve%20thousands%20of%20documents%20but%20you%20only%20rely%20on%2050%20of%20them.%20Accused%20may%20not%20remember%20every%20document.%20He%20may%20then%20ask%20that%20whatever%20document%20has%20been%20recovered%20from%20my%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20lawyer%20said%20the%20accused%20has%20a%20list%20of%20documents%20and%20cannot%20ask%20for%20them%20unless%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdesirable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20modern%20times%2C%20suppose%20he%20applies%20for%20documents%20running%20into%20thousands%20of%20pages.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%2C%20can%20easily%20be%20scanned%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Btimes%20are%20changing%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20us%20and%20advocates%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20we%20have%20objective%20to%20do%20justice.%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20be%20so%20rigid%20that%20the%20person%20is%20facing%20prosecution%20but%20we%20go%20and%20say%20that%20the%20documents%20are%20protected%3F%20Will%20this%20be%20justice%3F%20There%20are%20cases%20so%20heinous%20where%20bail%20is%20given%2C%20but%20nowadays%20people%20are%20not%20getting%20bail%20in%20Magistrate%20cases.%20Times%20are%20changing.%20Can%20we%20as%20this%20bench%20be%20so%20rigid%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20an%20accused%20has%20the%20right%20to%20seek%20documents%20if%20he%2Fshe%20relies%20on%20them%20to%20seek%20bail%20or%20dismissal%20of%20the%20case.%20Mr%20Raju%20contested%20this.%20%26quot%3BNo%20there%20is%20no%20right%20as%20such...%20He%20can%20request%20the%20court%20to%20look%20into%20this.%20Suppose%20there%20is%20no%20document%20as%20such%20and%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20conviction%20and%20he%20only%20wants%20to%20delay%20the%20trial%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20a%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20reserved%20the%20judgment%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMLA%20has%20repeatedly%20come%20under%20the%20lens%20after%20several%20high-profile%20Opposition%20leaders%20were%20arrested%20by%20central%20agencies%20under%20the%20anti-corruption%20law.%20While%20granting%20bail%20to%20Prem%20Prakash%2C%20allegedly%20an%20aide%20of%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20last%20month%2C%20the%20court%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BRelying%20on%20the%20judgment%20in%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20we%20have%20said%20that%20even%20in%20PMLA%20(Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act)%2C%20bail%20is%20a%20rule%20and%20jail%20the%20exception.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20referred%20to%20Section%2045%20of%20the%20PMLA%20that%20mentions%20twin%20conditions%20for%20bail%20--%20there%20should%20be%20prima%20facie%20satisfaction%20that%20the%20accused%20has%20not%20committed%20the%20offence%20and%20that%20he%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20commit%20any%20offence%20while%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20Section%2045%20specifies%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20is%20that%20the%20conditions%20must%20be%20met%20for%20bail.%20%26quot%3BLiberty%20of%20the%20individual%20is%20always%20the%20rule%20and%20deprivation%2C%20by%20procedure%20established%20by%20law%2C%20the%20exception.%20Twin%20test%20does%20not%20take%20away%20this%20principle%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725449520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-can-we-be-so-rigid-top-court-grills-central-agency-in-documents-case-6489135%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20tough%20questions%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20questioning%20if%20the%20agency's%20refusal%20to%20provide%20the%20accused%20with%20documents%20seized%20during%20a%20money%20laundering%20probe%20does%20not%20violate%20the%20right%20to%20liberty%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-new