0great%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20Baliga%20tells%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20his%20invention%20of%20the%20IGBT%20semiconductor%20device%20has%20made%20its%20way%20into%20the%20wider%20world%20of%20electronics%2C%20delivering%20electrical%20efficiency%20and%20helping%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20in%20everything%20from%20medical%20devices%20and%20consumer%20appliances%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplug-in-hybrid-prices-soaring-demand-electric-cars-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20it%20helped%20earn%20him%20a%20place%20in%20the%20National%20Inventors%20Hall%20of%20Fame.%20Now%20he's%20become%20the%20latest%20recipient%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmillenniumprize.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMillennium%20Technology%20Prize%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%201%20million%20euro%20(%241.1%20million)%20award%20presided%20over%20by%20the%20president%20of%20Finland%20that%20spotlights%20innovations%20beneficial%20to%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20capstone%20for%20my%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223375%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Professor%20Bantval%20Jayant%20Baliga.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d720cc14a5cd1fcc8c9ab7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225063%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProfessor%20Baliga%20has%20won%20several%20prizes%20following%20his%20invention%20of%20the%20IGBT.%3Cp%3EMillennium%20Technology%20Prize%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBaliga's%20career%20started%20as%20an%20undergraduate%20student%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20in%20Madras%2C%20where%20%E2%80%94%20like%20so%20many%20others%20of%20his%20time%20%E2%80%94%20he%20became%20enthralled%20with%20the%20legendary%20lectures%20delivered%20by%20physicist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F20-physicists-revolutionized-understanding-world-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERichard%20Feynman%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20California%20in%20the%201960s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20in%20my%20curriculum%2C%20but%20in%20our%20bookstore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20read%20when%20other%20students%20were%20going%20to%20the%20movies.%20It%20just%20inspired%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20a%20doctorate%20in%20electrical%20engineering%20in%20the%20US%20led%20to%20an%20initial%20role%20at%20General%20Electric%2C%20where%20he%20spent%20his%20time%20working%20in%20the%20world%20of%20transistors%20and%20thyristors%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20semiconductor%20industry%20was%20%26quot%3Balready%20considered%20very%20mature%2C%26quot%3B%20Baliga%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262aab9d7-0dc2-4e6c-954f-52618818ea5d%5C%22%3EFast%20track%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20that%20meant%20a%20big%20breakthrough%20would%20be%20tough%20to%20come%20by%2C%20he%20was%20full%20of%20ideas%20that%20could%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%2C%20particularly%20on%20how%20electrical%20efficiency%20could%20be%20improved%20in%20the%20full%20roster%20of%20products%20his%20employer%20was%20working%20on.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20pitch%20to%20Welch%2C%20Baliga%20was%20given%20the%20rare%20opportunity%20to%20fast-track%20a%20nascent%20idea%20from%20a%20research%20phase%20straight%20into%20manufacturing%20on%20a%20production%20line%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcern%20about%20global%20warming%20then%20was%20far%20less%20acute.%20However%2C%20it%20later%20became%20clear%20that%20reducing%20the%20electrical%20consumption%20of%20devices%20with%20IGBTs%20%E2%80%94%20found%20in%20everything%20from%20CAT%20scanners%20and%20microwaves%20to%20refrigeration%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Friding-japans-bullet-trains-between-tokyo-kyoto-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan's%20bullet%20trains%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20would%20have%20a%20huge%20positive%20downstream%20impact%20on%20carbon%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bullet%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F59a82fd62488494c425c361b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIGBTs%20can%20be%20found%20in%20everything%20from%20domestic%20appliances%20to%20bullet%20trains.%3Cp%3Egui%20jun%20peng%20%2F%20Shutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Baliga's%20own%20calculations%2C%20IGBTs%20have%20helped%20reduce%20global%20carbon%20emissions%20by%20more%20than%2082%20gigatons%2C%20or%20180%20trillion%20points%2C%20between%201990%20and%202020%20through%20reduced%20electrical%20energy%20and%20fuel%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo-thirds%20of%20the%20electricity%20in%20the%20world%20is%20used%20to%20run%20motors%20in%20consumer%20and%20industrial%20applications%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Professor%20P%C3%A4ivi%20T%C3%B6rm%C3%A4%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20International%20Selection%20Committee%20of%20the%20Millennium%20Technology%20Prize.%20%26quot%3BProfessor%20Baliga's%20innovation%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20develop%20societies%20with%20electricity%20efficiently%2C%20while%20dramatically%20reducing%20energy%20consumption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaliga%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20as%20a%20professor%20at%20North%20Carolina%20State%20University%20since%20his%20time%20at%20General%20Electric%2C%20knows%20there's%20more%20work%20to%20be%20done%20to%20ensure%20the%20world%20of%20electronics%20and%20semiconductors%20reduces%20electricity%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20Baliga%20sees%20the%20world%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fais-rapid-growth-threatens-energy-industry-economy-and-climate-1033552538%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intell