%26quot%3BHow%20Can%20House%20Be%20Demolished...%26quot%3B%20Court%20On%20'Bulldozer%20Justice'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav's%20'bulldozer'%20digs%20came%20hours%20after%20a%20key%20observation%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20questioned%20the%20idea%20of%20'bulldozer%20justice'%20and%20wanted%20to%20know%20how%20a%20building%20could%20be%20demolished%20simply%20because%20it%20belongs%20to%20an%20accused%2C%20or%20even%20a%20convict%2C%20in%20a%20criminal%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20observation%20was%20significant%20given%20the%20frequency%20with%20which%20BJP-ruled%20states%20bulldozed%20buildings%20of%20individuals%20accused%20in%20criminal%20cases%3B%20recent%20examples%20cited%20in%20court%20included%20the%20demolition%20a%20home%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Jaipur%20because%20the%20owner's%20son%20had%20stabbed%20a%20classmate.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20took%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20the%20controversial%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BIs%20Land%20For%20His%20Residence%20Approved%3F%26quot%3B%20Yadav's%20Jibe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20afternoon%20Mr%20Yadav%20followed%20up%20Tuesday's%20jab%20with%20a%20pointed%20question%20at%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%2C%20demanding%20an%20apology%20from%20the%20state%20for%20houses%20and%20buildings%20bulldozed%20till%20now%2C%20and%20suggested%20the%20BJP%20change%20its%20name%20to%20Bhartiya%20Jogi%20Party.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20so%20many%20names%20(of%20cities%20and%20towns%20in%20UP)%20have%20been%20changed%2C%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20should%20change%20name%20of%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20too...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20also%20threw%20in%20a%20cheeky%20side-swipe%20by%20asking%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20the%20land%20on%20which%20his%20home%20has%20been%20built%20meets%20regulatory%20requirements.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20scared%20others%2