ds%2C%20they're%20buying%20houses.%20And%20we're%20doing%20not%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20are%20almost%20100%25%20confident%20they%20won't%20have%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ccb82fe-046f-4494-a132-337cd620cc72%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20couple%20relied%20on%20their%20networks%20to%20get%20jobs%20after%20traveling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20May%20rolled%20around%2C%20after%20about%20five%20months%20on%20the%20road%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20to%20feel%20uneasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20the%20money%20running%20out%2C%20and%20we%20were%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20now%20we%20have%20to%20adult%20again%20and%20think%20about%20our%20return%20home%2C'%26quot%3B%20Hynes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20were%20worried%20about%20navigating%20a%20tough%20job%20market%2C%20it%20felt%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eless%20nerve-racking%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethan%20when%20Hynes%20had%20returned%20from%20her%20last%20big%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20further%20in%20your%20career%2C%20it%20actually%20makes%20it%20easier%20coming%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20big%20network%20of%20people%20to%20tap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20month%20of%20applying%20while%20abroad%2C%20the%20couple%20secured%20jobs%20and%20were%20able%20to%20negotiate%20start%20dates%20for%20their%20return%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20honest%20about%20her%20career%20break%20during%20the%20interview%20and%20hiring%20process%20worked%20in%20her%20favor%2C%20Hynes%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20people%2C%20like%2C%20'Yes%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20travel%20for%20six%20months.%20I%20feel%20extremely%20rejuvenated%2C%20and%20I'm%20very%20excited%20to%20work%20again%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20impressed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20seamless%20as%20their%20return%20to%20Canada%20was%2C%20adjusting%20to%20having%20a%20routine%20again%20hasn'