stories%2Fstunning-celebrity-pregnancy-photoshoots%2Fphotostory%2F113059407.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Relief%20Yet%20For%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20'Emergency'%2C%20She%20Claims%20Court%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKangana%20Ranaut's%20movie%20'Emergency'%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20massive%20row%20after%20Sikh%20organisations%20opposed%20its%20release%2C%20got%20no%20relief%20from%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20today.%20The%20court%20said%20it%20cannot%20ask%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC)%20to%20issue%20a%20certificate%20to%20the%20film's%20makers%20as%20it%20would%20contradict%20a%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20setback%2C%20the%20actor%20and%20BJP%20MP%20claimed%20a%20win%20in%20court.%20%26quot%3BHigh%20court%20has%20blasted%20censor%20for%20illegally%20withholding%20the%20certificate%20of%20%23emergency%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20is%20co-produced%20by%20Ms%20Ranaut's%20Manikarnika%20Films%20and%20Zee%20Studios.%20With%20the%20film%20earlier%20scheduled%20for%20a%20release%20on%20September%206%2C%20Zee%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%20approached%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20Censor%20Board%20to%20issue%20the%20certificate%20that%20would%20clear%20the%20decks%20for%20the%20film's%20release.%20The%20setback%20in%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20means%20that%20the%20movie%20is%20unlikely%20to%20release%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranaut-emergency-release-date-sensitive-content-government-sources-6473532%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSensitive%20Content%26quot%3B%3A%20Government%20Sources%20On%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20'%3Ci%3EEmergency%3C%2Fi%3E'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201975%2C%20ran%20into%20trouble%20after%20the%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee%2C%20the%20apex%20religious%20body%20for%20Sikhs%2C%20alleged%20that%20it%20misrepresents%20Sikhs%20and%20sought%20a%20ban.%20Ms%20Ranaut%20later%20said%20the%20Censor%20Board%20had%20put%20on%20hold%20the%20certificate%20issued%20to%20her%20film.%20Sources%20in%20the%20government%20said%20some%20religious%20organisations%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20film.%20%26quot%3BReligious%20sentiments%20cannot%20be%20hurt.%20There%20is%20some%20sensitive%20content%20in%20the%20movie%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Centre%20was%20seriously%20looking%20at%20the%20concerns.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-stuck-in-massive-row-what-are-the-objections-6487046%5C%22%3EKangana%20Ranaut's%20'Emergency'%20Stuck%20In%20Massive%20Row.%20What%20Are%20The%20Objections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20Sikh%20organisations%20filed%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20against%20the%20movie%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court.%20In%20its%20response%2C%20the%20Censor%20Board%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20movie%20had%20not%20been%20issued%20a%20certificate.%20The%20court%20then%20disposed%20of%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguing%20the%20matter%20in%20court%2C%20Zee's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Venkatesh%20Dhond%2C%20told%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BP%20Colabawalla%20and%20Justice%20Firdosh%20Pooniwalla%20that%20CBFC%20informed%20Manikarnika%20Films%20on%20August%208%20that%20film%20is%20suitable%20for%20unrestricted%20public%20exhibition%2C%20subject%20to%20some%20modifications.%20On%20August%2014%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20film's%20makers%20submitted%20the%20film%20to%20CBFC%20with%20the%20modifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2029%2C%20Manikarnika%20received%20an%20email%20from%20CBFC%20stating%20that%20the%20CD%20is%20sealed%20and%20requested%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20to%20collect%20the%20certificate.%20But%20later%2C%20the%20certificate%20was%20not%20handed%20over%2C%20apparently%20following%20the%20opposition%20from%20Sikh%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhond%20agued%20that%20CBFC%20is%20a%20censor%20body%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20an%20authority%20to%20look%20after%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20maker%20of%20the%20film%20is%20a%20sitting%20MP.%20They%20gave%20her%20a%20censor%20certificate%20and%20could%20have%20simply%20said%2C%20look%20we%20have%20given%20the%20censor%20certificate%20and%20now%20if%20there%20is%20unrest%2C%20the%20State%20can%20take%20care%20of%20the%20same.%20They%20cannot%20say%20that%20now%20that%20there%20is%20an%20unrest%2C%20we%20will%20rethink%20the%20certification.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20CBFC%2C%20Advocate%20Abhinav%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20certificate%20is%20not%20issued%20until%20it%20is%20signed%20by%20the%20Censor%20Board's%20chairperson.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20cannot%20ask%20CBFC%20to%20issue%20the%20certificate%20as%20it%20would%20be%20in%20breach%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20rejected%20CBFC's%20contention%20that%20the%20certificate%20had%20not%20been%20issued%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20makers%20comply%20with%20the%20modifications%20required%20by%20the%20CBFC%20and%20the%20CD%20with%20modifications%20is%20sealed%20successfully%2C%20we%20have%20to%20presume%20that%20the%20CBFC%20applied%20its%20mind%20and%20thereafter%20issued%20the%20email%20to%20Manikarnika%20that%20the%20CD%20of%20the%20film%20is%20successfully%20sealed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court's%20order%20was%20based%20on%20the%20Centre's%20submission%20that%20the%20film%20isn't%20certified%20yet%20and%20that%20it%20is%20under%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20relief%20to%20the%20film's%20makers%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20unable%20to%20pass%20this%20direction%20in%20light%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20MP%20High%20Court%20has%20specifically%20directed%20the%20CBFC%20to%20consider%20the%20representations%20of%20the%20Jabalpur%20Sikh%20Sangat%20before%20certifying%20the%20film.%20If%20we%20were%20to%20direct%20the%20CBFC%20to%20issue%20the%20certificate%2C%20we%20would%20have%20breached%20the%20division%20bench's%20directive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudicial%20Propriety%20demands%20such%20orders%20ought%20not%20be%20passed.%20We%20therefore%2C%20are%20unable%20to%20direct%20the%20CBFC%20to%20issue%20the%20certificate%20as%20sought%20by%20the%20petitioner.%20We%20however%2C%20do%20not%20dispose%20of%20the%20present%20petition.%20And%20we%20direct%20the%20CBFC%20to%20consider%20the%20objections%2C%20if%20any.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20the%20Board%20needs%20to%20consider%20other%20objections%20too%20and%20may%20take%20time%20to%20decide%20them%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20but%20you%20cannot%20keep%20it%20open%20ended.%20Movies%20are%20released%20on%20Fridays.%20There%20are%20crores%20and%20crores%20of%20money%20invested%20in%20this.%26quot%3B%20He%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BCBFC%20cannot%20be%20held%20ransom%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20asked%20CBFC%20to%20decide%20the%20representations%20before%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20September%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725441840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F84enior8_kangana-ranaut-emergency_625x300_02_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsetback-for-kangana-ranauts-emergency-in-high-court-no-censor-certificate-yet-6487467%22%2