%2C%20as%20per%20the%20charge%20sheet%20submitted%20in%20court%2C%20police%20sources%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20officers%20in%20the%20case%20have%20obtained%20information%20directly%20from%20Instagram%20to%20confirm%20this%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20sources%20said%20Renukaswamy's%20mobile%20was%20missing%20as%20the%20accused%20had%20allegedly%20thrown%20it%20into%20a%20canal%20while%20dumping%20the%20body%20of%20Renukaswamy%20after%20torturing%20him%20to%20death%20in%20June.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20had%20obtained%20a%20duplicate%20SIM%20card%20and%20got%20his%20social%20media%20accounts%20activated%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20police%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20civic%20authorities%2C%20and%20fire%20and%20emergency%20services%20personnel%20had%20launched%20an%20extensive%20search%20operation%20in%20the%20Vrushabhavathi%20canal%20to%20find%20the%20mobile%2C%20but%20were%20not%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20Renukaswamy%20developed%20hatred%20towards%20Darshan's%20partner%2C%20believing%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20had%20destroyed%20Darshan's%20family%20life%20and%20targeted%20her%20in%20support%20of%20his%20wife.%20Renukaswamy%20had%20allegedly%20sent%20a%20photograph%20of%20his%20genitals%20to%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20better%20than%20Darshan%2C%20according%20to%20the%20sources.%20He%20Renukaswamy%20also%20continued%20sending%20derogatory%20messages%20to%20Pavithra%20Gowda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20able%20to%20take%20the%20torture%2C%20Pavithra%20Gowda%20had%20informed%20Darshan's%20close%20associate%20Pavan%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20handle%20the%20situation%20without%20informing%20the%20superstar%2C%20sources%20said.%20However%2C%20Pavan%20had%20shared%20the%20information%20with%20Darshan.%20Enraged%20by%20this%2C%20Darshan%20had%20tasked%20Pavan%20to%20find%20out%20who%20thi